      "content": "but that's just what people say to make themselves feel better. i look at them and i see the stress in their eyes. every time i walk in the room, it's like they have to pretend everything is okay, but it isn't. if i was gone, the stress would go away. the money would stay in the family. it's like... isn't it more selfish to stay and keep dragging them down when you know you're the problem?",
